Create scanner for user input set to sc

Create condition for the end of While loop
	Set boolean loop equal to true
	
	Create while loop with the condition of loop
		Print out menu options 1 Encrypt, 2 Decrypt, and 3 Quit for switch case options.
		Initialized ch and equate it to user integer input
		
		Initialize switch case 1
			case 1 is used for Encryption
			initialize array digits
