			Until i is equal to four user inputs integers
			
			call array list from Encrypter class
				In encrypt method create 
				FOR loop until i equals 4, add 7 to digits[i]
				and mod digits[i] by 10
				END FOR
				
				set int odds equal to digits[0]
				set digits[0] equal to digits[2]
				set digits[2] equal to odds

				set int evens equal to digits[1]
				set digits[1] equal to digits[3]			
				set digits[3] equal to evens				
				return digits
				
			print encrypted results
			
		Initialize switch case 2
			case 2 is used for decryption
			initialize array digits
			print digits for encryption 
			
			Until i is equal to four user inputs integers
			
